  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: 1.9.8-stable\r\nOS & Version: OSX\r\n\r\n#### Feature Request\r\nCurrently when querying transactions using the GraphQL interface, there is no means to retrieve the signature parameters [R,S,V]. \r\n\r\nThe fields are necessary to calculate transaction hash and perform any validation on the returned results.  \r\n\r\nAre there any plans to add the support or I can submit a pull request\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
